            <thetext>The default cell renderer qx.ui.table.cellrenderer.Default checks the property &quot;useAutoAlign&quot; for &quot;boolean&quot; - a type that does not exists. So when trying to change that property, an Error will be thrown by the Property class.

SOLUTION
Check for &quot;Boolean&quot; - with upper case &quot;B&quot;.

Fabio</thetext>
